imports/raw/more_assets_to_ingest/sbs-cubemap-splitter-61b2c81e11ae/CSv1.0 README.txt,3092,ba9041315d6a99824662c795b5af5ca1ffcc02a11d266ced9d1fba9aeaa889f2,unknown_review_required,"Screaming Brain Studios - Cubemap Splitter v1.0 This tool has been released under the Public Domain (CC0) license and is free to share and redistribute. Open - Load a Cubemap, Panorama, or 6 images to stitch Layout - Switch the current projection type (Auto Detect, Horizontal, Vertical) Output - Displays the output folder where files will be saved. '...' - Select an output folder. Export - The two export buttons in the upper right will change depending on the current loaded Cubemap or Panorama image. The dark vertical bar between the two preview areas can be dragged and resized. Splitting a Cubemap / Panorama ------------------------------ Press the 'Open' button at the top right of the program. The Cubemap Splitter can load *.jpg, *.jpeg, *.bmp, *.png, or *.hdr Horizontal Cubemaps, Vertic"
